WEBVTT

00:00:26.513 --> 00:00:31.202
It started around 9am
and it went for 11 hours.

00:00:31.226 --> 00:00:35.322
(Phone) SVH: Or you always have the option
to exchange it for something else.

00:00:35.346 --> 00:00:36.710
AdG: Eleven hours?

00:00:37.403 --> 00:00:38.553
On the phone?

00:00:39.776 --> 00:00:42.090
I'm ready to give up after 11 minutes.

00:00:42.720 --> 00:00:45.870
Can you imagine wasting
your whole day on a helpline?

00:00:46.546 --> 00:00:48.736
What could possibly take that long?

00:00:49.450 --> 00:00:52.047
(Phone) SVH: And Chandler's like,
"What are you doing?"

00:00:52.071 --> 00:00:54.756
And he's like, "You said
I had to give you the chair --"

00:00:54.780 --> 00:00:57.828
AdG: In this case, Stephanie
and her customer spent the whole day

00:00:57.852 --> 00:00:59.410
talking about TV.

00:00:59.434 --> 00:01:02.204
(Phone) Woman: That's by far
my favorite episode.